                     </decoNote>
                    <decoNote type="frame" xml:id="d7">
                      Decorative designs:
                      <locus target="#1r" facs="003">fol. 1r</locus> (red, blue and black <foreign xml:lang="gez">ሐረግ፡</foreign>);
                      <locus target="#72r #76v #81v" facs="074 079 083">72r, 76v, 81v</locus> (red and black <foreign xml:lang="gez">ሐረግ፡</foreign>);
